/-
  STATUS: DISCOVERY
  AGENT: R4 Agent 3
  DIRECTION: The impossibility-theorem implication poset — its reduction backbone,
             transitive-reduction skeleton, and cross-level separation.

  SUMMARY:
    R3_Agent5_IndependenceMap proved that the UNIQUE intra-T.18 implication chain
    is T.18.6 ⟹ T.18.5, all other T.18 pairs being jointly-provable-but-independent.
    This file goes DEEPER and WIDER by incorporating the IT.5–IT.14 hardness family
