    SEPARATION WITNESS (R3_Agent5 joint-provability idiom).  `it7_it8_jointly_but_
    levels_distinct` exhibits ONE problem that is simultaneously Π⁰₂-hard (IT.7
    route) and Σ⁰₂-hard (IT.8 route) under their two *separate* reducibilities,
