  Depends on (imports + exact lemma names used):
    • MIP.Results.IT5_AtomicBarrierCoNPHard  : IT5_transfer
    • MIP.Results.IT11_PreorderCoNPHard      : IT_11_transfer
    • MIP.Results.IT7_BehaviorPi2Complete    : IT7_hard_transfer
    • MIP.Results.IT8_CeSigma2Complete       : IT8_hard_transfer
    • MIP.Results.IT13_SigmaStarUnique       : IT_13_hardness_transfer, Pi1Reduces,
                                               Pi1Reduces_trans, Pi1Reduces_refl
    • MIP.Results.IT14_MultiYW1Hard          : IT_14_hardness_transfer
